Referring to FIG. 1 the following main components of a nebulizer 1 are illustrated:
2, integral plastics housing body,
3, liquid supply chamber (or “reservoir”),
4, aerosol delivery tubular outlet,
5, aerosol generator assembly,
6, retainer, supporting the aerosol generator 5 in the integral housing body 2;
20, reservoir tubular top part,
21, reservoir funnel-shaped lower part (“funnel”),
22, liquid supply chamber cap;
23, cap tubular opening,
24, cap silicone plug,
30, power conducting pin support part of the housing body 2;
31, 32 conducting pins extending through the pin support housing part 30;

The dimensions of the gasket 48 are in this case, when relaxed:
internal diameter, 6.2 mm;
external diameter, 14.7 mm;
maximum depth, 2.1 mm;
height of ridges 74 and 75, 0.3 mm;
height of ridge 71 with respect to the body 70, 0.6 mm.
